headline: Live Nation Stock Among Biggest S&P 500 Gainers as BofA Lifts Price Target
summary: Live Nation Entertainment was one of the biggest gainers in the S&P 500 on Monday after Bank of America analysts lifted their price target for the entertainment stock.
